#: .\text\special-notes-RE.cfg:4
msgid " This unit can not be slowed for long due to it's sheer size."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special-notes-RE.cfg:7
msgid " This unit regenerates itsself when standing on hills or mountains."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special-notes-RE.cfg:10
msgid " This unit regenerates itsself when standing in the forest."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special-notes-RE.cfg:13
msgid " The medical knowledge allows this unit to rid itsself of poison."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special-notes-RE.cfg:16
msgid " Darkillumination slightly decreases the lighting level in adjacent areas."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special-notes-RE.cfg:19
msgid " Darkillumination decreases the lighting level in adjacent areas."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special-notes-RE.cfg:22
msgid " This unit is able to hide at night, leaving no trace of its presence."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special-notes-RE.cfg:25
msgid ""
" This unit can use it's shield to get a bonus physical resistance while "
"defending."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special-notes-RE.cfg:28
msgid ""
" In swampland, this unit’s ambush skill renders it invisible to enemies "
"unless it is immediately adjacent or has revealed itself by attacking."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special-notes-RE.cfg:31
msgid ""
" This unit’s marksmanship gives it a high chance of hitting targeted enemies,"
" but only at night."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special-notes-RE.cfg:34
msgid " This unit has a superior vision, allowing it to hit its target more often."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special-notes-RE.cfg:37
msgid ""
" This unit’s dextery always gives it a good chance of hitting targeted "
"enemies."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special-notes-RE.cfg:40
msgid " This unit can call upon bannishing magic, which has always 50% to hit."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special-notes-RE.cfg:43
msgid ""
" The strenght of this unit's weapon is so big, it recoils, lowering the "
"accuracy of each attack."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special-notes-RE.cfg:46
msgid ""
" The Deathstrike allows this unit to deal a lot of damage in one hit, but "
"only at night, or when the enemy is distracted."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_DEADLY_STRIKE
#: .\text\special_notes-BEEM.cfg:6
msgid " This unit has a 6% chance to kill immediately a lower level enemy."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_CAVESTALK
#: .\text\special_notes-EE.cfg:6
msgid ""
" In underground terrain (except lit underground), this units ambush skill "
"renders it invisible to enemies unless it is immediately adjacent or has "
"revealed itself by attacking."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_ACCURATE
#: .\text\special_notes-EoC.cfg:4
msgid ""
" This unit can attack more accurately, giving it a better chance to hit agile"
" foes on the offense."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_PHYSICAL_ENDURANCE
#: .\text\special_notes-EoC.cfg:7
msgid ""
" This unit will instantly regenerate half of the damage deal on it with "
"non-arcane attacks, unless it would otherwise kill it."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_HEAT_ABSORPTION
#: .\text\special_notes-EoC.cfg:10
msgid ""
" This unit will recover 5 HP per turn when on lava, sandy or desert terrain. "
"The effects of poison will not be prolonged or cured."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_AQUATIC_BODY
#: .\text\special_notes-EoC.cfg:13
msgid ""
" This unit will recover 5 HP per turn when on watery terrain. The effects of "
"poison will not be prolonged or cured."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_SYLVAN_REVITILIZATION
#: .\text\special_notes-EoC.cfg:16
msgid ""
" This unit will recover 5 HP per turn while in a forest or mushroom grove "
"terrains. The effects of poison will not be prolonged or cured."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_EARTH_RECUPERATION
#: .\text\special_notes-EoC.cfg:19
msgid ""
" This unit will repair its body with the rocks found while in/on hills, "
"caves, or mountains, thus recovering 5 HP in the process. The effects of "
"poison will not be prolonged or cured."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_ICE_CONVALESCENCE
#: .\text\special_notes-EoC.cfg:22
msgid ""
" This unit will recover 5 HP per turn while on snowy or icy terrain. The "
"effects of poison will not be prolonged or cured."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_CAMOUFLAGE
#: .\text\special_notes-EoC.cfg:25
msgid ""
" On desert terrain, this unit can use its camouflage skill to remain hidden "
"from enemies, unless they are standing next to it."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_DAUNTLESS
#: .\text\special_notes-EoM.cfg:6
msgid ""
" The steadiness of this unit reduces damage from some attacks, but only while"
" attacking."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_VAMPIRE_PLAGUE
#: .\text\special_notes-EoM.cfg:9
msgid ""
" Foes who lose their life to the bite of this noble vampire will rise again "
"as bloodborns, unless they are standing on a village."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_VAMPIRE
#: .\text\special_notes-EoM.cfg:12
msgid " Vampires are immune to drain and plague but are still susceptible to poison."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_BLOOD_HULK
#: .\text\special_notes-EoM.cfg:15
msgid " Blood Hulks can't advance to another unit, but they get a stronger bonus."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_MALBORN
#: .\text\special_notes-EoM.cfg:18
msgid " Malborns can't advance to another unit, but they get a stronger bonus."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_AE_PROTECTION
#: .\text\special_notes-EoMa.cfg:6
msgid ""
" This unit emits a protecting aura causing friendly units next to it to "
"defend better, taking less damage in combat."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_GURU
#. SPECIAL_NOTES_SUMMON_ROC
#. SPECIAL_NOTES_SUMMON_LVL3
#. SPECIAL_NOTES_SUMMON_LVL4
#. SPECIAL_NOTES_SUMMON_HS
#. SPECIAL_NOTES_MOF
#. SPECIAL_NOTES_MOW
#. SPECIAL_NOTES_MOA
#: .\text\special_notes-EoMa.cfg:9
#: .\text\special_notes-EoMa.cfg:12
#: .\text\special_notes-EoMa.cfg:15
#: .\text\special_notes-EoMa.cfg:18
#: .\text\special_notes-EoMa.cfg:21
#: .\text\special_notes-EoMa.cfg:24
#: .\text\special_notes-EoMa.cfg:27
#: .\text\special_notes-EoMa.cfg:30
msgid ""
" this unit can create other units in the near free spaces, but not in "
"villages."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_DIVINE_HEALTH
#: .\text\special_notes-EoS.cfg:6
msgid ""
" Due to this units relationship with its deity it is granted a magical body "
"in which the magic is manifested as self-healing and thus this unit recovers "
"3 HP per turn."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_DIVINE_HEALTH_ENHANCED
#: .\text\special_notes-EoS.cfg:9
msgid ""
" Due to this units relationship with its deity it is granted a magical body "
"in which the magic is manifested as self-healing, this is enhanced by this "
"units blood thirsty lifestyle and thus this unit recovers 6 HP per turn."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_MINOTAUR_HEAL
#: .\text\special_notes-EoS.cfg:12
msgid ""
" This unit will heal its allies by 5 HP per turn, however it will only "
"prolong the effects of poison not cure it."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_FLY
#: .\text\special_notes-EoS.cfg:15
msgid ""
" This unit can fly over the terrain and over any impediments such as the "
"snow, chasms and sand."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_SWAMP_PROWL
#: .\text\special_notes-EoS.cfg:18
msgid ""
" This unit can hide in swamps, and remain undetected by its enemies. Enemy "
"units cannot see this unit while it is in a swamp, except if they have units "
"next to it, and any enemy unit that first discovers this unit immediately "
"loses all its remaining movement."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_LEECH
#: .\text\special_notes-EoS.cfg:21
msgid ""
" This unit drains health from weaker living units, healing itself for half "
"the amount of damage it deals (rounded down).\n"
"It only work on Level 0 Units, on attack."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_DELUMINATES
#: .\text\special_notes-EoS.cfg:25
msgid ""
" This unit darkens the surrounding area, making chaotic units fight better, "
"and lawful units fight worse."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_BATTLE_TUTOR
#: .\text\special_notes-EoS.cfg:28
msgid ""
" This unit will give advice on battle tactics and whatnot to its allies, thus"
" the unit that was given the advice will gain extra XP whenever it gains XP "
"in battle."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_SOULBIND
#: .\text\special_notes-EoS.cfg:31
msgid ""
" A unit slain by this units Soulbinding attacks will have its soul trapped in"
" the caster's spell, thus is forced to serve the caster as an undead minion."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_TAME
#: .\text\special_notes-EotF.cfg:6
msgid " This unit can tame creatures as it levels up."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_SHALLOWSUB
#: .\text\special_notes-EotF.cfg:9
msgid ""
" This unit can move unseen in shallow and deep water, requiring little air "
"from the surface."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_BEACHHOME
#: .\text\special_notes-EotF.cfg:12
msgid ""
" This unit is at home on the beach, and can move undetected in any sandy area"
" or oasis."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_SIDHE_SPIRIT
#: .\text\special_notes-IE.cfg:6
msgid ""
" Spirits have very unusual resistances to damage, and move quite slowly over "
"open water."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_RUNELAYING
#: .\text\special_notes-IE.cfg:9
msgid ""
" A unit with runelaying will, at the beginning of its turn, place a rune on "
"its current hex that provides a random bonus to the unit on that hex."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_HIGHGROUND
#: .\text\special_notes-ME.cfg:6
msgid " When on a higher terrain, this unit can deal more damage with its bow."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_ARSON
#: .\text\special_notes-ME.cfg:9
msgid ""
" If the enemy is on flammable terrain, this unit can deal more damage, or "
"less, if the enemy is in water or swamp."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_TRIPLESTRIKE
#: .\text\special_notes-ME.cfg:12
msgid " This unit has an attack which hurts bystanders of a battle by 2."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_GROUPING
#: .\text\special_notes-ME.cfg:15
msgid ""
" When being adjacent to other units with grouping, this unit's damage "
"increases for each of them."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_BLOCK
#: .\text\special_notes-ME.cfg:18
msgid " This unit increases the resistances of nearby units by 20."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_PLAGUE_HIVE_GNAT
#: .\text\special_notes-ME.cfg:21
msgid ""
" Foes who lose their life to this unit will become infested and release a "
"Hive Gnat unless they are standing on a village, or are non living."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_PLAGUE_SLAV
#: .\text\special_notes-ME.cfg:24
msgid ""
" Foes who are defeated by this unit are taken as slaves unless they can hide "
"in a town. Slavers have little interest in the undead or constructs as they "
"know not how to control them."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_CONCENTRATED
#: .\text\special_notes-ME.cfg:27
msgid ""
"This unit must concentrate its weapon on the enemy, and its damage increases "
"by 1 with each successful hit."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_CURSED
#: .\text\special_notes-ME.cfg:30
msgid ""
" This Unit uses a cursed weapon which drains 2 hp of his lifepoints everytime"
" it strikes"
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_LATCH
#: .\text\special_notes-ME.cfg:33
msgid " This unit attaches to enemies when it hits them"
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_SPORES
#: .\text\special_notes-ME.cfg:36
msgid " This unit sprays spores nearby after using this ability."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_SUICIDE
#: .\text\special_notes-ME.cfg:39
msgid " This Unit dies instantly when it strikes."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special_notes-ME.cfg:41
msgid ""
" This units extremely long weapon allows it to group even better, although if"
" there are more units shortspeared grouping units helping a unit, his spear "
"will be ineffective due to crowding.(This unit adds +2 damage to units with "
"grouping, his effect does not mix with grouping effect, but does with Support"
" i.e. if there is 1 supporter but 3 groupers, it will take the higher effect "
"available to grouping.)."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special_notes-ME.cfg:43
msgid ""
" This units extremely long weapon allows it to group even better, although if"
" there are more units shortspeared grouping units helping a unit, his spear "
"will be ineffective due to crowding.(This unit adds +4 damage to units with "
"grouping, his effect does not mix with grouping effect, but does with Support"
" i.e. if there is 1 supporter but 3 groupers, it will take the higher effect "
"available to grouping.)."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special_notes-ME.cfg:45
msgid ""
" This units large number of javelins allows it to hand extra javelins to "
"those it is grouping with, allowing them to throw more javelins at a time. "
"Grouping units don't have enough room on their person to carry many javelins,"
" so they can only recieve javelins from one supplier."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special_notes-SH.cfg:6
msgid ""
"This unit has an attack which, if it hits an enemy unit, will halve that "
"units movement at the beginning of its next turn."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special_notes-SH.cfg:9
msgid "This unit has a leadership effect on all mechanical units."
msgstr ""

#: .\text\special_notes-SH.cfg:12
msgid ""
"This unit drains energy with some of its attacks. This drain is most "
"effective against mechanical units and has no effect on the undead."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_DREAD
#: .\text\special_notes.cfg:6
msgid ""
" The dread attack of this unit, when used offensively scare the defender, "
"lowering the damage of his retaliation."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_DEFEND_ONLY
#: .\text\special_notes.cfg:9
msgid " Some of this unit’s attacks are only available during defense."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_ATTACK_ONLY
#: .\text\special_notes.cfg:12
msgid " Some of this unit’s attacks are only available during offense."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_DISTRACT
#: .\text\special_notes.cfg:15
msgid ""
" This unit is capable of distracting opponents, allowing friendly units to "
"trespass their Zones of Control and move unhindered around them."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_PROTECTION
#: .\text\special_notes.cfg:18
msgid ""
" The importance of this unit motivates friendly units next to it to defend "
"better, taking less damage in combat, though this only applies to units of "
"lower level."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_TERROR
#: .\text\special_notes.cfg:21
msgid ""
" The terror skill of this unit scares enemy units next to it so they deal "
"less damage in combat, though this only applies to units of lower or equal "
"level."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_RALLY
#: .\text\special_notes.cfg:24
msgid ""
" Rally gives a bonus to surrounding units if this unit has made an attack "
"this turn, or, on defending, on its previous turn."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_RAGE
#: .\text\special_notes.cfg:27
msgid ""
" Whenever its rage attack is used, this unit will push the attack for several"
" rounds longer than normal."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_FORMATION
#: .\text\special_notes.cfg:30
msgid ""
" This unit works well with other units who can move in formation. When "
"adjacent to such units, this unit will take reduced damage from physical "
"attacks."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_COUNTER
#: .\text\special_notes.cfg:33
msgid ""
" While defending this units counter attacks will always have at least 60% "
"chance to hit."
msgstr ""

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_LOW_UPKEEP
#: .\text\special_notes.cfg:36
msgid " This unit costs 1 less gold worth of upkeep than it would normally."
msgstr ""

