#: .\units\archaic_units\despair\Widow_Banshee.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Banshees are either the ghosts of notable or high-born women, or at least "
"spirits interested in the lives of the high-born. Their appearance is taken "
"as a sign that someone is going to die, usually with good reason."
msgstr ""

