#: .\units\archaic_units\despair\Widow_Midnight.cfg:4
msgid "Midnight Beauty"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_despair_Midnight_Beauty, race=AE_arc_race_despair, gender=female
#: .\units\archaic_units\despair\Widow_Midnight.cfg:50
msgid ""
"Some ghosts mingle with the living during the day and evening, partaking of "
"the life they themselves were denied. They appear as beautiful women, and can"
" charm the young and foolish into escorting them home at night. Those that "
"head into the night with one of the Midnight Beauties are never seen again."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_despair_Widow_in_White, race=AE_arc_race_despair, gender=female
#: .\units\archaic_units\despair\Widow_White.cfg:4
msgid "Widow-in-White"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_despair_Widow_in_White, race=AE_arc_race_despair, gender=female
#: .\units\archaic_units\despair\Widow_White.cfg:18
msgid ""
"From a distance, a Widow-in-White almost looks like a regular human. But up "
"close, one can see that their skin and eyes are very pale and show no signs "
"of life. They wear a white dress and veil, as if in memory of their wedding "
"day and happier times."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_despair_Wisp, race=AE_arc_race_despair_wisp
#: .\units\archaic_units\despair\Wisp.cfg:4
msgid "Wisp"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_despair_Wisp, race=AE_arc_race_despair_wisp
#: .\units\archaic_units\despair\Wisp.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Wisps are something that is less of a human ghost, more of an evil spirit. "
"They float through the cold air, sucking the life out of those who face off "
"against the ghosts of the north, softening them up for the angry wights with "
"a more human form."
msgstr ""

