#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_phantom_Wing_Dancer, race=AE_arc_race_phantom_egypt, gender=female
#: .\units\archaic_units\phantom\Tomb_Wing.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Higher priestesses of the strange sword-dance are fearsome warriors, but they"
" still have the same ability to feignt and distract the opponent so that they"
" can slip through gaps in enemy formations."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Celebrant, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Celebrant.cfg:4
msgid "Primevalist Celebrant"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Celebrant, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Celebrant.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Though their faith in the Primeval beings has not flagged, their faith in "
"their own ability to bring the necessary pain to the enemy has (some would "
"say these are the wisest of all the Primevalists). They have instead turned "
"their attention to supporting their more confident brothers and have pursued "
"basic healing knowledge."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Celebrant.cfg:42
msgid "condemnation"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Fanatic, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Fanatic.cfg:4
msgid "Primevalist Fanatic"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Fanatic, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Fanatic.cfg:17
msgid ""
"When blind devotion is combined with combat experience, a more valuable "
"figher is formed. They know enough to be dangerous, but not enough to be "
"reasoned with."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Fighter, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Fighter.cfg:4
msgid "Primevalist Fighter"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Fighter, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Fighter.cfg:17
msgid ""
"The primevalists are mostly angry young men. The Dark Messiah told them what "
"they needed to hear to pick up a sword and attack their fellow humans in some"
" misguided attempt to please the Primevals. Upon joining the movement, each "
"fighter and follower is given a tattoo that is supposed to ward off evil "
"spirits."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Follower, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Follower.cfg:4
msgid "Primevalist Follower"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Follower, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Follower.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Some of the angry young men recruited by the Dark Messiah are more clever "
"than they are strong. These followers have some minimal magical training and "
"put it to use against their fellow humans in some misguided attempt to please"
" the Primevals. Upon joining the movement, each fighter and follower is given"
" a tattoo that is supposed to ward off evil spirits."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=cold, range=ranged
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Follower.cfg:37
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Monk.cfg:37
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Prior.cfg:45
#: .\units\archaic_units\south-seas\Caster.cfg:40
msgid "chill"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Leader, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Leader.cfg:4
msgid "Primevalist Leader"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Leader, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Leader.cfg:18
msgid ""
"While the Primevals most likely have as little respect for these warriors as "
"they do for any human, the other fanatics admire their dedication to the "
"(unfortunate) faith they all share. Some of this admiration is due to a "
"unique ability: Whether it is a gift granted by the Primeval Ones or just the"
" ability of a focused mind, no one can say - but the Leaders can cause a "
"piercing pain in the enemy with the wave of a hand..."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Leader.cfg:43
msgid "soul-pierce"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Monk, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Monk.cfg:4
msgid "Primevalist Monk"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Monk, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Monk.cfg:18
msgid ""
"The followers continue to study magic and the glyphs carved into stone by the"
" Primevals long ago. Most of the glyphs' meaning is obscure, and the "
"Primevals don't appear interested in explaining anything, but this makes the "
"Monks work harder than ever to be deemed worthy."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Prior, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Prior.cfg:4
msgid "Primevalist Prior"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Prior, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Prior.cfg:17
msgid ""
"The hardiest and most clever of the glyph readers extract the most knowledge,"
" and gain great attack power to bring glory to their sect."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Prior.cfg:36
msgid "staff base"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Sun_Shield, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Shield-High.cfg:4
msgid "Primevalist Sun-Shield"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Sun_Shield, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Shield-High.cfg:18
msgid ""
"These fighters play a supporting role, stoically absorbing damage so that "
"their more hot tempered commrads survive long enough to accomplish their "
"goals. Their armour disipates heat and cold and energy blasts, so they have "
"higher than average resistance to fire, cold, and arcane damage."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Brightshield, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Shield.cfg:4
msgid "Primevalist Brightshield"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Primevalist_Brightshield, race=AE_arc_race_human_primevalist
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primevalist_Shield.cfg:107
msgid ""
"These fighters play a supporting role, stoically absorbing damage so that "
"their more hot tempered comrades survive long enough to accomplish their "
"goals. Their armour is designed to disipate heat and cold and energy blasts, "
"so they have higher than average resistance to fire, cold, and arcane damage."
" They can form a very effective defensive line, but they are not expected to "
"make a good strike force."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Aerowheel, race=AE_arc_race_primeval, gender=female
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primeval_Aerowheel.cfg:4
msgid "Aerowheel"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Aerowheel, race=AE_arc_race_primeval, gender=female
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primeval_Aerowheel.cfg:38
msgid ""
"Having mastered the cutting wheel, a Primeval Ironwheel must make a choice "
"whether to focus on the disc weapon or to tend to other skills required of a "
"high ranking soldier. Primeval Aerowheels have chosen the latter and are "
"mixed fighters, and somehow they can predict magical attacks dodging them "
"more often.\n"
"Special Note:"
msgstr ""

