#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primeval_Dogface.cfg:4
msgid "Dogface"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Dogface, race=AE_arc_race_primeval
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primeval_Dogface.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Like the experienced chakram throwers, the Primeval soldiers wear some sort "
"of visor. Though it simply looks like a piece of metal strapped across the "
"eyes, the visor appears to assist the fighter in targeting the enemy."
msgstr ""

