#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primeval_Driver.cfg:4
msgid "Driver"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Driver, race=AE_arc_race_primeval
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primeval_Driver.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Primeval Drivers are not that much smaller than a Troll. They have risen out "
"of the Slowfoot ranks through strength and experience. With enough luck and "
"determination, they might be able to escape their caste and join the ranks of"
" the Line Breakers."
msgstr ""

