#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_primeval_Firewheel, race=AE_arc_race_primeval, gender=female
#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primeval_Firewheel.cfg:38
msgid ""
"Having mastered the cutting wheel, a Primeval Ironwheel must make a choice "
"whether to focus on the disc weapon or to tend to other skills required of a "
"high ranking soldier. Primeval Fire have chosen the first and are ranged "
"specialists at refusing all physical armor and throwing at fores cutting or "
"burning chakrams. They are also known to be very resilient to cold and heat "
"but it is unknown from where this come from.\n"
