#: .\units\archaic_units\primeval\Primeval_Velite.cfg:17
msgid ""
"The Velites are the weakest and lowest-ranking of the Primeval males. They "
"are denied the chance to join the proper warrior class, but they are used as "
"spear-carrying light infantry."
msgstr ""

