msgid "Able-Seaman"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_south_seas_Able_Seaman, race=AE_arc_race_south_seas_human, gender=male
#: .\units\archaic_units\south-seas\Able-Seaman.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Though not Captains, Able-Seaman are higher ranking than the bulk of the "
"sailors and have more access to resources. In these times of conflict, they "
"have melted some of the lead normally used for ballast and affixed it to the "
"end of a staff to create something similar to a hammer."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_south_seas_Albatross, race=gryphon, gender=male
#: .\units\archaic_units\south-seas\Albatross.cfg:4
msgid "Albatross"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_south_seas_Arsonist, race=AE_arc_race_south_seas_human, gender=male
#. [unit_type], id=AE_ext_outlaws_Arsonist, race=human, gender=male
#. [unit_type], id=AE_mrc_refugees_Arsonist, race=AE_mrc_refugees_race
#: .\units\archaic_units\south-seas\Arsonist.cfg:4
#: .\units\EE_units\outlaws\Outlaw_Arsonist.cfg:5
#: .\units\ME_units\refugees\c2-arsonist.cfg:5
msgid "Arsonist"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_south_seas_Arsonist, race=AE_arc_race_south_seas_human, gender=male
#: .\units\archaic_units\south-seas\Arsonist.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Ships are a very important part of life in the South Seas, so if one wanted "
"to ruin a successful member of society, they would destroy their ships. The "
"Arsonists are employed for this purpose. They operate at night, to avoid "
"shoreman and sailors."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_south_seas_Lore_Caster, race=AE_arc_race_south_seas_human, gender=female
#: .\units\archaic_units\south-seas\Caster.cfg:4
msgid "female^Lore-Caster"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_south_seas_Lore_Caster, race=AE_arc_race_south_seas_human, gender=female
#: .\units\archaic_units\south-seas\Caster.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Lore-Casters study the old teachings and lore from days long ago. That may "
"seem academic and irrelevant to life at sea, however South-Seas ships that "
"carry Lore-Casters tend to survive longer at sea. Some attribute this to "
"their knowledge of how to placate the gods."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_south_seas_Deck_Master, race=AE_arc_race_south_seas_human, gender=male
#: .\units\archaic_units\south-seas\Deck-Master.cfg:4
msgid "Deck-Master"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_south_seas_Deck_Master, race=AE_arc_race_south_seas_human, gender=male
#: .\units\archaic_units\south-seas\Deck-Master.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Because they are not wealthy, Deck-Masters will never own a ship of any size,"
" but they are trusted on the larger vessals to keep the rest of the men in "
"line. They have affixed steel grapples to the ends of the staves, and can use"
" them to hook the opponent's weapon."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=melee
#: .\units\archaic_units\south-seas\Deck-Master.cfg:57
msgid "hook"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_south_seas_Demolitionist, race=AE_arc_race_south_seas_human, gender=male
#: .\units\archaic_units\south-seas\Demolitionist.cfg:4
