#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_south_seas_Diver, race=AE_arc_race_south_seas_human
#: .\units\archaic_units\south-seas\Divers.cfg:39
msgid ""
"Divers are oftenly employed to scare away sharks in ports. A throw of their "
"harpoon usually is enough to scare away a shark. Also in war, harpoon can be "
"used as a disabling weapon if aimed in the right spot."
msgstr ""

