#: .\units\archaic_units\south-seas\Salvager.cfg:20
msgid ""
"The Salvagers are less concerned with the loading and unloading of ships, and"
" focus their efforts on the more lucrative job of salvage. They break apart "
"old ships and sell what can be sold. Long lances are useful in prodding "
"floating wood, as well as poking hostile forces."
msgstr ""

