#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_south_seas_Wrecker, race=AE_arc_race_south_seas_human, gender=male
#: .\units\archaic_units\south-seas\Wrecker.cfg:4
msgid "Wrecker"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_south_seas_Wrecker, race=AE_arc_race_south_seas_human, gender=male
#: .\units\archaic_units\south-seas\Wrecker.cfg:21
msgid ""
"The Wreckers are the most experienced of the salvagers. They usually operate "
"alone, which maximizes both the profit and danger, so they carry harpoons to "
"fight off sharks, thieves, and other Wreckers."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_ukians_Royal_Constable, race=human
#: .\units\archaic_units\ukians\Royal_Constable.cfg:4
msgid "Constable"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_ukians_Northern_Fighter, race=human
#. [unit_type], id=AE_fut_Nordhris_Northern_Fighter, race=AE_fut_race_Nordhris, gender=male
#: .\units\archaic_units\ukians\Royal_Fighter.cfg:4
#: .\units\EotF_units\Nordhris\Northern_Fighter.cfg:5
msgid "Northern Fighter"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_ukians_Northern_Fighter, race=human
#: .\units\archaic_units\ukians\Royal_Fighter.cfg:17
msgid ""
"The fighters of the North have heavy clothing and armour that make them "
"strong against cold and damage. It also makes them slow on their feet."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_ukians_Royal_FireKnight, race=human
#: .\units\archaic_units\ukians\Royal_FireKnight.cfg:4
msgid "Northern Fire-Knight"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_ukians_Royal_FireKnight, race=human
#. [unit_type], id=AE_arc_ukians_Royal_Rider, race=human
#: .\units\archaic_units\ukians\Royal_FireKnight.cfg:20
#: .\units\archaic_units\ukians\Royal_Rider.cfg:19
msgid ""
"The mounted patrol of the northern kingdom ride the sturdy equine peculiar to"
" the frozen north, and carry a pannier of smoldering coals. They use the "
"coals to keep warm on their long patrols, and also to heat branding irons. "
"The irons are intended for marking animals as the king's property, but they "
"also make decent weapons."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=fire, range=melee
#: .\units\archaic_units\ukians\Royal_FireKnight.cfg:55
#: .\units\archaic_units\ukians\Royal_Horseman.cfg:53
