#: .\units\BEEM_units\wood_warriors\Terrible_Bigfoot.cfg:19
#: .\units\BEEM_units\wood_warriors\Young_Bigfoot.cfg:18
msgid ""
"This unit is from BEEM. Its coding and art were done by Voodoo, Baro_st, "
"Tydeus, Dibs, and various others.\n"
"\n"
"There aren't many bigfoot in the world so it's difficult to see the few ones."
" Unbeatable masters in hiding among trees, these creatures can be 2mts tall "
"in the adultness and they are both among the mildest and the most powerful "
"warriors the forests have ever seen. Completely covered with a thick fur, "
"Bigfoot usually dislike fighting but for a good reason. However, they are "
"very protective of their territory and their kicks can easily floor also the "
"most resistant warriors. It's told Bigfoot can live a thousand year and the "
"older ones are so great and strong to uproot trees with extreme easiness."
msgstr ""

