msgid "Exiled Alchemist"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_bem_wood_warriors_Exiled_Alchemist, race=AE_bem_wood_warriors_race, gender=male
#. [unit_type], id=AE_bem_wood_warriors_Legendary_Sorcerer, race=AE_bem_wood_warriors_race, gender=male
#. [unit_type], id=AE_bem_wood_warriors_Woods_Druid, race=AE_bem_wood_warriors_race, gender=male
#: .\units\BEEM_units\wood_warriors\Exiled_Alchemist.cfg:18
#: .\units\BEEM_units\wood_warriors\Legendary_Sorcerer.cfg:20
#: .\units\BEEM_units\wood_warriors\Wood's_Druid.cfg:19
msgid ""
"This unit is from BEEM. Its coding and art were done by Voodoo, Baro_st, "
"Tydeus, Dibs, and various others.\n"
"\n"
"These human warriors at the beginning are young alchemists who, banished from"
" their native villages having broken the law or having practiced forbidden "
"magic, are forced to live in the woods as fugitives. Ever wanted, they have "
"to rob the travelers to survive. Living in symbiosis with nature, Exiles "
"usually become druids. In addition to their extraordinary power, exiles are "
"able to prepare potions and mixtures which can heal every type of wounds, "
"including poison-based ones.The older ones acquire uncommon wisdom and "
"knowledge. Some of them become powerful wizards able to use both fire and "
"arcane spells with great skill, throwing fireballs and lightning bolts from "
"their staffs, which are real symbols of their power."
msgstr ""

