"Tydeus, Dibs, and various others.\n"
"\n"
"Fauns are mythological creatures who live in perfect symbiosis with nature; "
"this particularity makes them among the most deadly assassins who live in the"
" forest. Their body is similar to the human one, but they have some "
"zoomorphic element.You can immediately see it looking at their legs, similar "
"to the sheep's ones, which they also took the fur from which covers them up "
"to the belly.Most of them like to use the powerful means nature gave them, or"
" at most bows built by them. They dislike to use cutting weapons, used only "
"by monarchs."
msgstr ""

