#. [race], id=AE_chs_faerie
#: .\units\EoC_units\faeries.cfg:8
msgid ""
"Forests, caverns, mountains, and large bodies of water are propitious places "
"to find many kinds of rare and mysterious creatures. Such environments are "
"thus preferred by the remnants of the peoples said to antedate civilized life"
" on Irdya, such as woses and merfolk, and the varied group of beings more "
"commonly known as the true faeries."
msgstr ""

