#. [unit_type], id=AE_chs_sylvians_Sprite, race=AE_chs_faerie, gender=female
#: .\units\EoC_units\faeries\Fire_Sprite.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Mischievous in nature, these fiery faeries are pranksters at heart with a "
"sense of humor that is often called nymph-like. While their command of the "
"fire element remains a mystery, it has been rumored that these faeries are "
"cousins to the imp. However, their protective attitude of nature and "
"whimsical personality make them fast friends to the elves."
msgstr ""

