msgid ""
"The people of Theria are known for their pursuit of spirituality. The Therian"
" have also learned to greatly respect nature from their neighbors the Warg. "
"Many Therian attune their spirits to animals which they revere. These Therian"
" are capable of harnessing their inner spiritual power to shift into the "
"animal to which they are attuned.\n"
"\n"
"Therian who value grace, swiftness, and majesty attune to the falcon.  Falcon"
" Therian can travel great distances when in their shifted form, though are "
"not the strongest in combat."
msgstr ""

