"Many Therian attune their spirits to animals which they revere. These Therian"
" are capable of harnessing their inner spiritual power to shift into the "
"animal to which they are attuned.\n"
"\n"
"Therian who value strength, power, and intensity attune to the wild cats.  "
"These Therian are brutal in combat when in their attuned form, using their "
"claws, or sometimes even jaws, to shred their enemies and protect their "
"people."
