#. [unit_type], id=AE_myh_Therian_Apprentice, race=AE_myh_therian
#: .\units\EoM_units\therians\x1_Apprentice.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Therians are a peaceable people who enjoy quite study and contemplation. As "
"such there are many with magical talent about them. Their more varied studies"
" allow them to master both fire and ice, but not as well as people who learn "
"one or the other."
msgstr ""

