#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Kraken, race=AE_stf_triththa_cuttlefish
#: .\units\EOS_units\cuttlefish\Kraken.cfg:4
msgid "Kraken"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Kraken, race=AE_stf_triththa_cuttlefish
#: .\units\EOS_units\cuttlefish\Kraken.cfg:19
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
"\n"
"Cuttle Fish are gigantic creatures of the seas. This particular one is "
"covered in steel, which makes it a much stronger opponent. Thankfully, it "
"also makes it significantly slower."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Squid, race=AE_stf_triththa_cuttlefish
#: .\units\EOS_units\cuttlefish\Squid.cfg:4
msgid "Squid"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Squid, race=AE_stf_triththa_cuttlefish
#: .\units\EOS_units\cuttlefish\Squid.cfg:18
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
"\n"
"It is a time-honoured tradition to have bodies of water near dwarvish "
"settlements be guarded by tentacled creatures. Outsiders have oft questioned "
"the practicality and safety of such arrangements, but the dwarves of triththa"
" have learned that cuttlefish are quite intelligent and when raised from "
"birth, can be taught to follow orders.\n"
"\n"
"The trick to finding a young cuttlefish is knowing the colour of their shell."
" Young ones still have a softer and weaker one, that has a pinkish hue."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Arblaster, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Arblaster.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Arblaster"
msgstr ""

