msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
"\n"
""
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Arblaster, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Arblaster.cfg:20
msgid ""
"When the dwarves of Triththa turned to crossbows, it was only natural that "
"they would apply their famed craftsmanship and push the design to its very "
"limit. The result is the arblast, a large crossbow made mostly out of steel "
"that fires with tremendous force and great accuracy."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Armorer, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Armorer.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Armorer"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Armorer, race=dwarf
#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Ballista, race=mechanical
#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Compounder, race=dwarf
#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Crossbowman, race=dwarf
#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Plainsrider, race=mechanical
#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Repeater, race=dwarf
#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Smith, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Armorer.cfg:19
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Ballista.cfg:20
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Compounder.cfg:17
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Crossbowman.cfg:17
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Plainsrider.cfg:17
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Repeater.cfg:18
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Smith.cfg:18
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
" \n"
""
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Armorer, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Armorer.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Dwarvish armorers are the driving force behind the great dwarven armies, "
"supplying the fighters with their weapons. An Armorer can help nearby allies "
"to fight more effectively, though they can hold their own as well."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Ballista, race=mechanical
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Ballista.cfg:5
msgid "Dwarvish Ballista"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Ballista, race=mechanical
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Ballista.cfg:22
msgid ""
"The ultimate crossbow, a ballista is almost guaranteed to kill anything that "
"is hit by one of its massive bolts. It is a large and cumbersome weapon, but "
"dwarves somehow manage to move it over mountains and even through caves.\n"
"\n"
"The operators of ballistae like to tinker with their machines, which has a "
"wide variety of results."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Charger, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Charger.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Charger"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Charger, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Charger.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Charging at an enemy with only a shield is dangerous business and though "
"charges are sometimes necessary, chargers expand their weaponry with a "
"standard axe, allowing them a safer way to fight."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Compounder, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Compounder.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Compounder"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Compounder, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Compounder.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Compounder is the name given to these dwarves by their orcish enemies. It is "
"unknown what the reason for this name is, though it probably has to do with "
"their weapons, which are much more powerful than an ordinary crossbow.\n"
"\n"
"Some speculate that the sole reason orcish clans keep invading Triththa is to"
" supply their troops with dwarvish weapons, weapons of a quality they are "
"unable to match."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Crossbowman, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Crossbowman.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Crossbowman"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Crossbowman, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Crossbowman.cfg:19
msgid ""
"With the knowledge of a thunderstick's creation long lost due to lack of lack"
" of materials and needing a ranged weapon, the dwarves of Triththa turned to "
"more conventional weapons."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Defender, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Defender.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Defender"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Defender, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Defender.cfg:26
msgid ""
"The pinnacle of dwarvish Guards, defenders carry specially crafted runic "
"shields, making them almost impossible to dislodge from any position they "
"have taken, even by magic users."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Guard, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Guard.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Guard"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Guard, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Guard.cfg:25
msgid ""
"It is after numerous battles that an experienced Shieldman is awarded the "
"title of Guard and is charged with protecting ever more important assets of "
"Triththa. Their increasing skill makes that removing a Guard from his "
"emplacement is no easy task."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Linebreaker, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Linebreaker.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Linebreaker"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Linebreaker, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Linebreaker.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Easily as skilled ordinary fighters with the axe, linebreakers are difficult "
"to remove from the positions they so quickly occupy. When necessary, they "
"live up to their name, breaking apart defensive lines with well-placed "
"charges."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Plainsrider, race=mechanical
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Plainsrider.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Plainsrider"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Plainsrider, race=mechanical
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Plainsrider.cfg:19
msgid ""
"While going through mountains, dwarvish runners are matched in speed only by "
"birds, on flat ground though, their small stature limits their pace. So when "
"requirements arose for long-range reconnaissance across vast stretches of "
"flatlands, a new tool was needed, and dwarvish engineers invented this:\n"
"\n"
"Balanced in a lightweight steel chassis connecting four wheels is a wooden "
"cabin just large enough to house a dwarf. Moving at high speed, it runs of "
"the dwarf's own strength plus another source that the engineers of Triththa "
"are unwilling to disclose even to their brethren. Though it makes for a light"
" vehicle, the size of the machine limits the occupant's weaponry to a small "
"axe and a similar sized, slow-loading but powerful crossbow."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Repeater, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Repeater.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Repeater"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Repeater, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Repeater.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Many have speculated about the mysterious devices or magics that allow "
"dwarves to fire these weapons as fast as elves can fire their bows. Whatever "
"the cause, the result is an instrument that spews death at a terrifying rate."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Runefighter, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Runefighter.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Runefighter"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Runefighter, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Runefighter.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Though many fighters choose to outfit themselves with steel armor, some pick "
"a different path and focus their attention on weaponry. Specifically, runic "
"weaponry that almost always finds its target."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Runefighter.cfg:32
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Runewarrior.cfg:31
msgid "runic axe"
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Runefighter.cfg:44
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Runewarrior.cfg:43
msgid "runic hammer"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Runewarrior, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Runewarrior.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Runewarrior"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Runewarrior, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Runewarrior.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Given the expense and effort of carving runes, it is rare to see them on "
"projectile weaponry. Only the greatest of dwarven warriors will be seen "
"throwing runic axes at their enemies, a sight that is usually followed by the"
" death of the target."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=blade, range=ranged
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Runewarrior.cfg:55
msgid "runic hatchet"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Rusher, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Rusher.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Rusher"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Rusher, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Rusher.cfg:20
msgid ""
"The fastest dwarves are tasked with racing to important positions and holding"
" them while the rest of the army catches up. Should the location already be "
"occupied, they usually attempt to bash their opponent out of the way with "
"their shield."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Shieldman, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Shieldman.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Shieldman"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Shieldman, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Shieldman.cfg:25
msgid ""
"The dwarves of Triththa learned long ago that defending their land depended "
"on warriors that would hold the lines, even in open ground. Essential to this"
" are heavy shields that can be bashed into an opponent's face."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Smith, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Smith.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Smith"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_triththa_Smith, race=dwarf
#: .\units\EOS_units\dwarves\Smith.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Smiths are the craftsmen that make the technological marvels that the "
"dwarvish race is rightly so famous for. Though it is uncommon to see one in "
"battle, they wield their smithing hammers with unrelenting ferocity."
msgstr ""

