"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
"\n"
"Those not skilled with magic nor faithful enough who wish to be part of "
"Eltirean forces become the warriors. Of course it won't be on the flying "
"isles if there wasn't some magic included but the warriors use the magic in "
"the form of enchanted weapons and armor. The adepts in barracks are often "
"called the Glory skylords when they come to be trained."
msgstr ""

