msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Arcane_Archer, race=human, gender=female
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\ArcaneArcher.cfg:19
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
"\n"
"Although their weapons are not particularly potent against undead, Bowmaidens"
" occasionally find themselves placed in garrisons where the dead still "
"linger. A select group of maidens have chosen to forgo the  inhibitions of "
"Eventide and study magic other than that of light and darkness.For their "
"crimes they have been Stripped of their ability to cast light. These Archers "
"instead rely on their newfound knowledge of magic in order to fight."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\ArcaneArcher.cfg:49
msgid "arcane arrow"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Auxilary, race=human
#. [unit_type], id=AE_imp_Lavinians_Auxiliary, race=AE_imp_lavinian_race
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Auxilary.cfg:5
#: .\units\imperial_units\human-lavinians\Auxiliary.cfg:5
msgid "Auxiliary"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Auxilary, race=human
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Auxilary.cfg:18
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
" \n"
"Not all Eventide are warriors by nature. However, when the bells of war call "
"out every town under the Eventide's control still will send men and women to "
"bolster the defense of their nation. These untrained soldiers are given a "
"spear and often sent to hold positions away from the front line as a reserve "
"force."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Desperado, race=human
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Desperado.cfg:6
msgid "Desperado"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Desperado, race=human
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Desperado.cfg:18
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
" \n"
"The criminal and the insane are not wasted in Eventide society. Rather than "
"execute or lock up their dangerous individuals, they are used in the "
"military. Given cheap and easy to replace weapons, these Desperados make "
"exceptional scouts."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Diu_Bowmaiden, race=human, gender=female
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Diu_Bowmaid.cfg:5
msgid "Diu Bowmaiden"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Diu_Bowmaiden, race=human, gender=female
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Diu_Bowmaid.cfg:19
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
"\n"
"Carrying the light of day and the few remnants of honor that Diura embodied "
"into combat, these brave women grace the battlefield with their sliver-tipped"
" arrows. Graceful and durable, they nevertheless are not trained in melee "
"combat and fare poorly in close quarters."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Diu_Bowmistress, race=human, gender=female
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Diu_Bowmistress.cfg:5
msgid "Diu Bowmistress"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Diu_Bowmistress, race=human, gender=female
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Diu_Bowmistress.cfg:19
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
"\n"
"When a Bowmaiden has been recognized for her skill in archery, she is "
"stripped of her gray robe in a long ritual and presented with a robe of "
"silver and white. Normally this is done in the presence of her friends and "
"family, but often this formality is forgone while on the battlefield."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Diu_Keenshot, race=human, gender=female
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Diu_Keenshot.cfg:5
msgid "Diu Keenshot"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Diu_Keenshot, race=human, gender=female
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Diu_Keenshot.cfg:20
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
"\n"
"In every generation, only a handful of Bowmaidens have been recognized by "
"their peers as being exceptional in both ability and temperament. These few "
"are recognized by their peers as the paragon of their culture, and are gifted"
" a robe of pure gold thread to signify the brilliance that they bring with "
"them in every step."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Dreadlord, race=human, gender=male
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Dreadlord.cfg:5
msgid "Dreadlord"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Dreadlord, race=human, gender=male
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Dreadlord.cfg:20
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
"\n"
"Dreadlords harken back to the golden age, bringing back memories of the "
"brutal rule that the nobility of Noct used over their subjects before the "
"disaster. In person they are said to be relentless and terrifying. In combat,"
" this virtue is multiplied severalfold."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Eventide_Alchemist, race=human
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\EventideAlchemist.cfg:5
msgid "Eventide Alchemist"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Eventide_Alchemist, race=human
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\EventideAlchemist.cfg:18
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
"\n"
"When an Herbalist has proven his loyalty to the Eventide, his superiors will "
"offer to teach him the prized secret of the Alchemist's guild, how to make "
"'palmfire.' This potent substance can be spread across any weapon that will "
"not melt or burn, immediately setting aflame when it is struck soundly.\n"
"\n"
"Alchemists find themselves able to use this newfound weapon to great effect.\n"
""
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=fire, range=melee
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\EventideAlchemist.cfg:45
msgid "flaming sword"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Eventide_Herbalist, race=human
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\EventideHerbalist.cfg:5
msgid "Eventide Herbalist"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Eventide_Herbalist, race=human
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\EventideHerbalist.cfg:18
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
"\n"
"The second foe the Eventide faced in their fervor for revenge were the elves."
" Faced with an opponent to whom day and night ment nothing, the Eventide were"
" forced to find a new way to fight. One man, a local herbalist, suggested "
"that they use an extract from a particularily potent type of plant local to "
"their new home as a poison.\n"
"\n"
"From that time on, the Eventide have always had a select group of men who "
"have been trained from an early age in the proper use and application of said"
" poison. Members of this group would attack their enemies far away, with "
"knives."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Eventide_Poisoner, race=human
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\EventidePoisoner.cfg:5
msgid "Eventide Poisoner"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Eventide_Poisoner, race=human
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\EventidePoisoner.cfg:19
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
"\n"
"When faced with foes who have similarly eliminated their fear of both day and"
" night, the Eventide do not balk at using other means to achieve their goal "
"of complete conquest. From deep within (their cities), men and woman from "
"less scruptulous professions are enlisted, their ability with blades and "
"their knowledge of poison highly regarded in military use. "
msgstr ""

#. [heals], id=AE_stf_anti_poison
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\EventidePoisoner.cfg:33
msgid "Allows the unit to recover from the effects of poison"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Lineman, race=human, gender=male
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Lineman.cfg:5
msgid "Lineman"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Lineman, race=human, gender=male
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Lineman.cfg:19
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
"\n"
"Occasionally a lineman shows valor above and beyond his station. Offered a "
"commission and given a job as a full-time soldier (as well as a pension), "
"many Auxillaries who survive the brutal wars that (this faction) initiates "
"find themselves living a very comfortable life. Of course, that is provided "
"they live long enough to enjoy it."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Lineman.cfg:56
#: .\units\misc_units\frozen\FrostLanceman.cfg:58
#: .\units\misc_units\frozen\FrostSpearman.cfg:56
msgid "thrown spear"
msgstr ""

#. [female]
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Lineman.cfg:97
msgid "Linewoman"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Madcap, race=human
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Madcap.cfg:5
msgid "Madcap"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Madcap, race=human
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Madcap.cfg:18
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
" \n"
"Few Desperados escape death on the battlefield, however those few, rare, "
"tough-as-nails individuals are referred to by their peers and commanders as a"
" 'Madcap.'"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Mariner, race=human
#. [unit_type], id=AE_mrc_mercenaries_Mariner, race=AE_mrc_mercenaries_race
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Mariner.cfg:5
#: .\units\ME_units\mercenaries\g3-Mariner.cfg:5
msgid "Mariner"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Mariner, race=human
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Mariner.cfg:17
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
" \n"
"All members of the Eventide whose profession involves ships learn to swim "
"very well at a young age. In times of war, their swimming ability is often "
"put to the test. Although they feel comfortable on land, no Mariner ever "
"truly feels at home when not near the water."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Mariner.cfg:35
