#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Navigator, race=human
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Navigator.cfg:18
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
" \n"
"All members of the Eventide whose profession involves ships learn to swim "
"very well at a young age. In times of war, their swimming ability is often "
"put to the test. Although they feel comfortable on land, no Navigator ever "
"truly feels at home when not near the water."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Guardian_of_Noct, race=human, gender=male
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Noct_Guardian.cfg:5
msgid "Guardian of Noct"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Guardian_of_Noct, race=human, gender=male
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Noct_Guardian.cfg:20
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
"\n"
"Of all Noct soldiers, only a select elite who have proven their worth in a "
"multitude of battles are told deepest secrets of the Macelord order. Some say"
" it is a means of keeping the strongest on top of the macelord order, but "
"others claim that only the strongest of wills can bear to hear the secrets "
"kept from the common Eventide soldier."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Noct_Macelord, race=human, gender=male
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Noct_Macelord.cfg:5
msgid "Noct Macelord"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Noct_Macelord, race=human, gender=male
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Noct_Macelord.cfg:19
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
"\n"
"In Noct, the title of Macelord was only given to those who had shown "
"excellence in battle. In this fasion, the Eventide have maintained their "
"heritage and only give the title of Macelord to exceptional individuals."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Noct_Maceman, race=human, gender=male
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Noct_Maceman.cfg:5
msgid "Noct Maceman"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Noct_Maceman, race=human, gender=male
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Noct_Maceman.cfg:19
msgid ""
"This unit is from The Era of Strife. Its coding and art were done by Jami, "
"AI, Elrias, Lizard, Quietus, Espreon, Neorice and Various others.\n"
"\n"
"These ruthless warriors harken back to the terrible reign of the Noct "
"overlords, brutal nobles who used threats of punishments so terrible that "
"their armies would rather run headlong into combat than face their masters. "
"While this terrible method of invigorating troops has long been discarded by "
"the eventide, the reputation of a Noct Maceman has not. "
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_stf_eventide_Swabbie, race=human
#: .\units\EOS_units\eventide\Swabbie.cfg:5
