#. [unit_type], id=AE_fut_brungar_Apothecary, race=AE_fut_brungar_race, gender=male
#: .\units\EotF_units\brungar\Apothecary.cfg:5
msgid "Apothecary"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_fut_brungar_Apothecary, race=AE_fut_brungar_race, gender=male
#: .\units\EotF_units\brungar\Apothecary.cfg:19
msgid ""
"This unit is from the Era of the Future. Its coding, art, and ideas were done"
" by Turuk, Mirion147, Huston, Pentarctagon, Wesfreak, Xandria, and Zerovirus.\n"
"\n"
"Many Brungar lack the ability to weild magic skillfully and turn their "
"attention towards the various herbs and sea weeds that grow throughout their "
"domain. They study them for both their curative and poisonous properties. "
"While many have the healers touch and instinctively know which herbs to boil "
"and which to chew raw, there are some among the ranks of the Apothecary that "
"simply enjoy seeing their enemies fall from some unknown enemy lurking inside"
" their very bodies. The Apothecarys can be both a life saver and a life "
"sucker."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
#: .\units\EotF_units\brungar\Apothecary.cfg:38
msgid "Blow Dart"
msgstr ""

