msgid "Herbal Fumes"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_fut_brungar_Baby_Sea_Turtle, race=monster
#: .\units\EotF_units\brungar\Baby_Sea_Turtle.cfg:5
msgid "Baby Sea Turtle"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_fut_brungar_Baby_Sea_Turtle, race=monster
#: .\units\EotF_units\brungar\Baby_Sea_Turtle.cfg:19
msgid ""
"This unit is from the Era of the Future. Its coding, art, and ideas were done"
" by Turuk, Mirion147, Huston, Pentarctagon, Wesfreak, Xandria, and Zerovirus.\n"
"\n"
"Sea Turtles are a necessity of life for the sea-faring Brungar. Although the "
"majority of these docile reptiles are kept for food, it occassionally happens"
" that one of the oceanic testudines become a warsteed. These animals join the"
" Brungar army as what amounts to their adolescence. Their shells are "
"immediately painted according to the tribal color of their tamers, in order "
"to discern them from wild and enemy turtles. The bony shell of these turtles "
"are comparable in fortitude to the guardsmen of ancient times. The turtles "
"will bite antagonizing forces in close range, and can fire jets of water at "
"enemies when engaging in long-range combat."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: .\units\EotF_units\brungar\Baby_Sea_Turtle.cfg:31
#: .\units\EotF_units\brungar\Giant_Sea_Turtle.cfg:38
