#: .\units\EotF_units\Nordhris\Arctic_Prowler.cfg:35
msgid "Razor Claws"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_fut_Nordhris_Braveheart, race=AE_fut_race_Nordhris, gender=male
#: .\units\EotF_units\Nordhris\Braveheart.cfg:5
msgid "Braveheart"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_fut_Nordhris_Braveheart, race=AE_fut_race_Nordhris, gender=male
#: .\units\EotF_units\Nordhris\Braveheart.cfg:19
msgid ""
"This unit is from the Era of the Future. Its coding, art, and ideas were done"
" by Turuk, Mirion147, Huston, Pentarctagon, Wesfreak, Xandria, and Zerovirus.\n"
"\n"
"The Braveheart class are the most expendable units of the Nordhris military, "
"and as such, they form the vanguard of any Nordhris assault force. Those who "
"choose to enter into the Nordhris military as a Bravehearts, despite the "
"overwhelming odds of their death, are often regarded as either very "
"courageous or very stupid. The truth, however, is that most Bravehearts are "
"of the lower classes and join to escape the depressing realities of their own"
" situation in life; whether it be debt, starvation, homelessness, or "
"something else entirely. There is also another reason for joining: the sheer "
"number of deaths in their ranks mean that anyone who survives long enough "
"(sometimes only a few years) will be granted a position of leadership among "
"the Bravehearts - along the the amenities and status that comes with any "
"position of leadership in the military."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: .\units\EotF_units\Nordhris\Braveheart.cfg:27
#: .\units\EotF_units\Nordhris\Northern_Fighter.cfg:33
