msgid ""
"This unit is from the Era of the Future. Its coding, art, and ideas were done"
" by Turuk, Mirion147, Huston, Pentarctagon, Wesfreak, Xandria, and Zerovirus.\n"
"\n"
"Sometimes the snow runners with the most extraordinary vision would be picked"
" to become farseers. They wouldnt have to run as much as other scouts but "
"remain rather stationary providing information about their enemies from "
"distance, or providing a ranged support whenever it is needed."
msgstr ""

