#. [unit_type], id=AE_fut_Nordhris_Frenetic_Shaman, race=AE_fut_race_Nordhris, gender=male
#: .\units\EotF_units\Nordhris\Frenetic_Shaman.cfg:5
msgid "Frenetic Shaman"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_fut_Nordhris_Frenetic_Shaman, race=AE_fut_race_Nordhris, gender=male
#: .\units\EotF_units\Nordhris\Frenetic_Shaman.cfg:18
msgid ""
"This unit is from the Era of the Future. Its coding, art, and ideas were done"
" by Turuk, Mirion147, Huston, Pentarctagon, Wesfreak, Xandria, and Zerovirus.\n"
"\n"
"While they carry the name 'shaman', they bear almost no resemblance to their "
"elven counterparts. These shamans of the Nordhris have decided to focus all "
"of their time and effort to ridding the undead and their masters from the "
"world. The youngest and least experienced of them, the frenetic shaman, have "
"begun learning the intricacies casting arcane spells in order to undo the "
"evil magic that allows necromancers to animate corpses and bind souls to "
"their will. This is not enough, however. The shamans are also able to go into"
" a berserk frenzy at will, and are capable of taking down most enemy mages "
"with ease. It is almost solely due to the effort of these shamen that the "
"undead have been nearly eliminated from their lands and all of the "
"surrounding territories."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: .\units\EotF_units\Nordhris\Frenetic_Shaman.cfg:23
