#. [unit_type], id=AE_fut_welkin_Astral_Ranger, race=AE_fut_welkin, gender=male
#: .\units\EotF_units\welkin\Astral_Ranger.cfg:5
msgid "Astral Ranger"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_fut_welkin_Astral_Ranger, race=AE_fut_welkin, gender=male
#: .\units\EotF_units\welkin\Astral_Ranger.cfg:19
msgid ""
"This unit is from the Era of the Future. Its coding, art, and ideas were done"
" by Turuk, Mirion147, Huston, Pentarctagon, Wesfreak, Xandria, and Zerovirus.\n"
"\n"
"The Astral Ranger is probably one of the most talented soldiers in the Army "
"of Thoth, and also the most magical. This, along  with their odd outward "
"appearence, makes them unpopular among the Welkin. These Welkin have traveled"
" the land with their long  dark robes helping those in need. They carry no "
"weapons except a hammer of ice which they created with their skill as do the "
"lesser of their order. When found on the battlefield they often leave a trail"
" of the fallen who have been crushed by  their incredible hammer."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
#: .\units\EotF_units\welkin\Astral_Ranger.cfg:56
