msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_feu_clockwork_dwarves_Artillery, race=AE_feu_clockwork_dwarf
#: .\units\feudal_units\dwarves-clockwork\Artillery.cfg:4
msgid "Artillery"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_feu_clockwork_dwarves_Artillery, race=AE_feu_clockwork_dwarf
#: .\units\feudal_units\dwarves-clockwork\Artillery.cfg:18
msgid ""
"This unit is from Feudal Era. Its coding and art were done by Turin and "
"Various others.\n"
" \n"
"The dwarves most proficient with their 'guns' use even larger, more complex "
"ones. These artillerymen fire shells as big as a man's fist at the same rate "
"as their comrades fire smaller shells. Though not as a large as the rocks "
"flung by catapults, the dwarven artillery prove quite effective against "
"fortifications and troops alike."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
#. [attack], type=pierce, range=melee
#: .\units\feudal_units\dwarves-clockwork\Artillery.cfg:37
#: .\units\feudal_units\dwarves-clockwork\Gunner.cfg:35
