#. [race], id=AE_mrc_mutant_race
#: .\units\ME_units\cult.cfg:18
msgid ""
"The Mutants are a subrace of humans who have lived in the sewers of the Holy "
"Order as part of the cult. How they became mutants is unknown, but it is "
"expected that the Library of the Holy Order dumps magical byproducts into the"
" sewers which give them their lizardlike characteristics. The change is "
"generally slow and can sometimes take years. But by the end of the change "
"they can be considered similar to the extinct race of saurians and drakes "
"with their large powerful jaws, sharp claws, scaley skin, and tails. Some "
"mutants although not lizardlike in appearance have amazing lifespans which "
"last atleast 10 times that of the average human."
msgstr ""

