#. [race], id=AE_mrc_infernai_race
#: .\units\ME_units\infernai.cfg:7
msgid ""
"As the time of darkness came upon the land, monstrosities never seen by "
"humanity came from the Earth and spread across the lands. Of these atrocities"
" the Infernai were the worst. Though they were the most intelligent of the "
"three bringers of darkness, they were also the fiercest and most "
"bloodthirsty. They did not simply fight to eat, they fought for much more "
"crude reasons: To spread fear, enslave, maim, rend. They fought simply for "
"the fun of it, and did a *damn* good job."
msgstr ""

