#. [race], id=AE_mrc_djinn_race
#: .\units\ME_units\infernai.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Before the uprise of fanatasizm in the desert, there were many caravans who "
"traveled seeking great wealth. At the same time, some Oracle establishments "
"within the area had experiments with the capturing of souls. Through oracle "
"greed and fanatical trade, fanatic ancestors were given the secret to "
"entrapment of souls in bottles and lamps. Thus the djinn were created, souls "
"of average people were stored in bottles, enslaved for centuries. As time "
"passed and the apocalypse fell across the land enchanters found these bottles"
" hidden in trader caches, and felt pity for the poor souls. In exchange for "
"the souls explaining how to trap a soul in a bottle, or other inanimate "
"object, the enchanters imbued them with magical elemental powers, by placing "
"runes on the lamps, bottles, and so on. Thus the four elemental groups of "
"genie were formed. Djinn of Air, Ifreet of Fire, Genie of Water and Ice, and "
"Dao of Earth."
msgstr ""

