#. [unit_type], id=AE_mrc_enchanters_Cursedsword, race=AE_mrc_enchanters_race
#: .\units\ME_units\enchanters\c1-cursedsword.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Some enchanters specialize in crafting deadly swords that can be sharpened "
"easier than common steels and are lighter than usual with the cons that this "
"strange metal needs to consume a part of the living essence of the user in "
"order to not break down. Once the user dies poetically we can say the same "
"about the cursed sword itself at becoming into a regular sword which is "
"heavier than before when it was cursed."
msgstr ""

