msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_mrc_enchanters_Cursedhand, race=AE_mrc_enchanters_race
#: .\units\ME_units\enchanters\c2-cursedhand.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Cursedhand after some fighting experience and after understanding better how "
"cursed swords does work, they made a small modification to it, so now if they"
" consider necessary, their swords can now drain the living essence of the "
"rival as well but it is still consuming the user meanwhile. With those "
"modifications, the user himself loses some arcane and fire tolerance."
msgstr ""

