#: .\units\ME_units\holy_order\d2-judgementor.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Judgementors are next level of being a judiciary. They take the cases that "
"affect the royal family or any other form of government. To this day, noone "
"who has been judged by one of these fellows has had any other ruling "
"thereafter."
msgstr ""

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
